{"tid":19361,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[lihkg]整咗個睇圖同睇故網","createTime":"2016-12-02T17:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T14:18:04.000Z","uid":3399,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f3b36667a295abd58f258d62ca1bb58c2c3dd1","tid":19361,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lihkg.ho9su.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flihkg.ho9su.com&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=055c2f50\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.ho9su.com</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的,以前用HKG+睇圖雖然好方便,但始終手機MON細而且慢,多圖啲仲會彈APP,所以嗰陣已經想整,但自己覺得太複雜所以放棄<br />\n<br />\n依家LIHKG有API容易好多所以就試下整,如果ADMIN唔同意麻煩同我講,我會即STOP<br />\n<br />\n另外都有個追故模式,佢會搵哂樓主啲文出黎,但因為好多時作者會同讀者交流,所以特別SET咗如果個REPLY係引用人地就唔會出現<br />\n<br />\n至於點用呢其實都好簡單,入到去個LOGO下低果格就係用黎貼上條LINK或者POST ID,然後就根據你想追文定睇圖而去按下面既&quot;追故模式&quot;或者&quot;圖片模式&quot;,咁佢就會開始LOAD,可能會比較慢,請等一下,佢會自己跳頁,如果個POST比較多頁,佢就會分兩三次去處理,避免出現TIME OUT<br />\n<br />\n本來想將圖片模式入面啲圖CACHE落SERVER做埋打包,順便畀人追舊POST都唔怕死圖,<a href=\"http://但發現唔知點解如果張圖係UP咗去NA.CX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%96%E4%BF%82UP%E5%92%97%E5%8E%BBNA.CX&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=71abf533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但發現唔知點解如果張圖係UP咗去NA.CX</a>既話就會出現504 ERROR,DOWNLOAD唔到,所以無整到<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家高抬貴手,小弟PROGRAM唔係好得,希望大家唔好玩BUG,我都係想方便自己同大家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.ho9su.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flihkg.ho9su.com&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=055c2f50\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.ho9su.com</a>"},{"pid":"64b8329850488ee483ca27d8c2817c339b0e2baa","tid":19361,"uid":365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff265eb79de6fd109ac699db2eae7a9910b98399","tid":1936