kquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f21f29eb5b5d0747d22b731d6f213d6e6ea6b8f","tid":19361,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T20:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打可唔可以整埋自動將link變圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢層要再研究一下，整到就可以打睇埋bam圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暫時搵到方法整好咗,不過某啲情況下會廢咗,regex用極都唔明,有無巴打幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n另外因為BAM圖都SHOW埋所以頂嗰到戴咗頭盔,有無法律JJ解釋下有無用<br />\n<br />\n同埋追故模式加咗樓層可以直接跳落去"},{"pid":"78e00900bd41507c88c586c6916658a60e6b121f","tid":19361,"uid":17139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:00:58.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2689f916ff5b80f7a4abab58ae80ed75feba356d","tid":19361,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:34:51.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3802b41a461108129d5cfe600ab05fab1f796e","tid":19361,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:27:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c401a3d30c897c119ed5fb95cc91500a9e6ba0d3","tid":19361,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://除咗NA.CX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%99%A4%E5%92%97NA.CX&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=58fb62be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">除咗NA.CX</a>網之外,其他圖都會嘗試BACKUP"},{"pid":"88c